uthor_name": "藍天", "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106867464763719821092/reviews", "language": "zh-Hant", "original_language": "zh-Hant", "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUj20ccSZ0F9v5JKVEeiagFV9T21sDs68p1xI8j93Yyi-Nvxng=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba8", "rating": 4, "relative_time_description": "2 年前", "text": "這公園整理的蠻漂亮的，讓附近居民有一個休閒散步的好地方，真不錯。", "time": 1659117040, "translated": false}, {"author_name": "劉珍齡", "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106724237023149010185/reviews", "language": "zh-Hant", "original_language": "zh-Hant", "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW1CsyV7LTh9kvCvyQs9XPMYjazKVQIIkVQxxQKxPO5qjmxC4Pj=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba7", "rating": 4, "relative_time_description": "1 年前", "text": "從新店社福館旁邊的穿堂進入小公園，花木扶疏，乾淨又幽靜。", "time": 1703853575, "translated": false}, {"author_name": "Cindy Ding", "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112826584002439717902/reviews", "language": "zh-Hant", "original_language": "zh-Hant", "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVt4ksA5rWZp_2TflZ1G_AYMHZTg1su71FtUhl5yAuTH2WAtbs=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5", "rating": 5, "relative_time_description": "3 年前", "text": "很大的一座公園，適合民眾帶小孩、寵物來玩耍，也很適合運動、聊天。
